### Get all items
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items

### Get only lost items
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items?type=lost

### Get items by category
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items?category=electronics

### Search items
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items?search=phone

### Get a single item by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/items/64f5a53d9f83621c26506030

### Create a new lost item
POST http://localhost:5000/api/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "lost",
  "title": "Lost iPhone 14 Pro",
  "description": "Lost my black iPhone 14 Pro near Central Park. It has a blue case with my initials on it.",
  "category": "electronics",
  "location": {
    "address": "Central Park West",
    "city": "New York",
    "state": "NY",
    "coordinate": {
      "lat": 40.7812,
      "lng": -73.9665
    }
  },
  "images": ["https://example.com/placeholder-image.jpg"],
  "user": "64f5a53d9f83621c26506028"
}

